  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ancient magic circle has weakened, and monsters have appeared. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restore the magic circle with the Saint and stop the darkness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/6677497c809b3b7467d41346c471bf5e.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=800 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/6677497c809b3b7467d41346c471bf5e.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/6677497c809b3b7467d41346c471bf5e.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>’Save Me, My Hero’</strong> is a defense game with roguelike elements. Complete your own battle style with the hero's various skills and special abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your own hero.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your hero's abilities with various items and skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/35f47e8c4fb79069436eba013b25f4b6.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/35f47e8c4fb79069436eba013b25f4b6.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/35f47e8c4fb79069436eba013b25f4b6.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/0919c6788145ba588e67eacb5e5c7654.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/0919c6788145ba588e67eacb5e5c7654.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/0919c6788145ba588e67eacb5e5c7654.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d06a7fc3947247a2138ac883eb557336.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d06a7fc3947247a2138ac883eb557336.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/d06a7fc3947247a2138ac883eb557336.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even the same hero can fight differently depending on items and skills. Create your hero with various skills and items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/60d5b3cb12554777575100975e03dc8e.poster.avif?t=1738540789\" width=200 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/60d5b3cb12554777575100975e03dc8e.webm?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274350/extras/60d5b3cb12554777575100975e03dc8e.mp4?t=1738540789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><sp